title: Fargo the Pig
author: MaraLikesCookies
pages:
#- In Loving Memory Of Fargo the Pig. On May 3rd, 2014 I met Fargo for the first time. He was an awesome Pig so i decided to take him home. As soon as i got him home, he got used to our house very quickly. He roamed around and had the best time a pig could 

#- ever have. About 7 times a  day I feed him with delicious carrots grown daily at the Carbon Farm. He was happy until the next day. On May 4th, 2014 we made a great living space for Fargo. But after trying to get him in the pen, Fargo decided that it was 
#- enough. He commited suciced that day. he ran into the red firey flames and Killed himself. His last words were "Oink!!". We will always miss Fargo and will never get another pig like him.
#- 